com.snowplowanalytics.snowplow.tracker.events

Class AbstractEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.snowplowanalytics.snowplow.tracker.events.AbstractEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Event
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EcommerceTransaction, EcommerceTransactionItem, PageView, ScreenView, Structured, Timing, Unstructured

    public abstract class AbstractEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements Event
    Base AbstractEvent class which contains common elements to all events: - Custom Context: list of custom contexts or null - Timestamp: user defined event timestamp or 0 - Event Id: a unique id for the event - Subject: a unique Subject for the event
